{"tid":2233491,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"DW - 獨家：聯合國大會上的中國「戰狼」","createTime":"2020-10-07T07:17:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T04:21:12.000Z","uid":179729,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7eaf7564453a5995ea3ed0091ed61bc1c3157ff2","tid":2233491,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T07:17:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.dw.com/image/54172677_403.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fimage%2F54172677_403.jpg&h=2395838f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在39國發佈聲明譴責中國侵犯人權的同一天，數名外國外交官與德國之聲分享中國如何運用威脅攻勢，試圖防止各國簽署批判中國政策的聲明。<br />\n<br />\n「中國外交官會不斷出現在你面前。他們會不斷打電話給你丶傳訊息給你，不論是晚上或是週末。他們的攻勢從未間斷。」<br />\n<br />\n「他們會叫我到會場外，然後將我包圍住。基本上是一個三對一的情況，而且他們當下的行為非常有侵略性。」<br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"https://p.dw.com/p/3jXPf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp.dw.com%2Fp%2F3jXPf&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmSlkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=6561fab9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://p.dw.com/p/3jXPf</a>"},{"pid":"e1c4d6378bd62a716f5af713e50179f739a44a13","tid":2233491,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T07:17:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/dw_chinese/status/1313732493720408067?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdw_chinese%2Fstatus%2F1313732493720408067%3Fs%3D20&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmSlkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=cd57eb2d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdw_chinese%2Fstatus%2F1313732493720408067%3Fs%3D20&h=442e8cc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/dw_chinese/status/1313732493720408067?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"189cc83b33762a029c1e07500bfc15d41ec46632","tid":2233491,"uid":53498,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T07:18:18.000Z","msg":"「他們會叫我到會場外，然後將我包圍住。基本上是一個三對一的情況，而且他們當下的行為非常有侵略性。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n傳銷狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"